WEBVTT

00:00:06.825 --> 00:00:09.101
Zamislite tople, mekane kolače,

00:00:09.101 --> 00:00:10.513
krckave bombone,

00:00:10.513 --> 00:00:12.076
vazdušaste torte,

00:00:12.076 --> 00:00:14.693
kornete pune sladoleda.

00:00:14.693 --> 00:00:16.670
Ide li vam voda na usta?

00:00:16.670 --> 00:00:17.538
Želite li dezert?

00:00:17.538 --> 00:00:18.843
Zašto?

00:00:18.843 --> 00:00:19.924
Šta se događa u mozgu

00:00:19.924 --> 00:00:23.700
što slatku hranu čini tako neodoljivom?

00:00:23.700 --> 00:00:24.931
Šećer je zajednički naziv

00:00:24.931 --> 00:00:26.549
koji opisuje celu klasu molekula

00:00:26.549 --> 00:00:28.427
koji se zovu ugljeni hidrati

00:00:28.427 --> 00:00:31.278
i nalaze se u mnogim vrstama
hrane i pića.